item.title: CVE-2024-7861|2024-09-12T06:00:06.323Z -- unknown -- misiek%20paypal
item.description: The Misiek Paypal WordPress plugin through 1.1.20090324 does not have CSRF check in some places, and is missing sanitisation as well as escaping, which could allow attackers to make logged in admin add Stored XSS payloads via a CSRF attack.
